column2: You have re-organized and vassalized the [From.PrimaryTitle.GetName] of the historical Roman province under your command. May their mighty power help you fight off the barbarians!

column2: Without the authority of a Roman liege controlling their historical province, the [From.PrimaryTitle.GetName] has lost its roots and was forced to disbanded.
column3: Sans l'autorité d'un suzerain romain contrôlant leur province historique, la [From.PrimaryTitle.GetName] a perdu ses racines et a été forcée de se dissoudre.

column2: One day I shall reconquer these lands...
column3: Un jour je vais reconquérir ces territoires...

column2: Fine, I had no use for that Roman legacy.
column3: Bien, je n'avais aucune utilité de cet héritage Romain.
